{"id":439,"ayahs":[{"number":39,"arabic":"هُوَ ٱلَّذِى جَعَلَكُمْ خَلَٰٓئِفَ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ فَمَن كَفَرَ فَعَلَيْهِ كُفْرُهُۥ ۖ وَلَا يَزِيدُ ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ كُفْرُهُمْ عِندَ رَبِّهِمْ إِلَّا مَقْتًۭا ۖ وَلَا يَزِيدُ ٱلْكَٰفِرِينَ كُفْرُهُمْ إِلَّا خَسَارًۭا","translation":"He it is who has made you inherit the earth. Hence, he who is bent on denying the truth [of God’s oneness and uniqueness ought to know that] this denial of his will fall back upon him: for their [per­sistent] denial of this truth does but add to the deniers’ loathsomeness in their Sustainer’s sight and, thus, their denial of this truth does but add to the deniers’ loss.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3699.mp3","surahId":35,"words":[{"id":40903,"position":1,"arabic":"هُوَ","translation":"তিনিই (আল্লাহ)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40904,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40905,"position":3,"arabic":"جَعَلَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদেরকে বানিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40906,"position":4,"arabic":"خَلَـٰٓئِفَ","translation":"প্রতিনিধি হিসেবে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40907,"position":5,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40908,"position":6,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ ۚ","translation":"পৃথিবীর","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40910,"position":7,"arabic":"فَمَن","translation":"অতঃপর যে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40911,"position":8,"arabic":"كَفَرَ","translation":"অবিশ্বাস করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40912,"position":9,"arabic":"فَعَلَيْهِ","translation":"তার উপর তখন (পড়বে)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40913,"position":10,"arabic":"كُفْرُهُۥ ۖ","translation":"তার অবিশ্বাসের (শাস্তি)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40915,"position":11,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"এবং না","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40916,"position":12,"arabic":"يَزِيدُ","translation":"বৃদ্ধি করে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40917,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"কাফেরদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40918,"position":14,"arabic":"كُفْرُهُمْ","translation":"অবিশ্বাস তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40919,"position":15,"arabic":"عِندَ","translation":"কাছে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40920,"position":16,"arabic":"رَبِّهِمْ","translation":"তাদের রবের","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40921,"position":17,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40922,"position":18,"arabic":"مَقْتًۭا ۖ","translation":"ক্রোধ","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40924,"position":19,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40925,"position":20,"arabic":"يَزِيدُ","translation":"বৃদ্ধি করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40926,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلْكَـٰفِرِينَ","translation":"কাফেরদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40927,"position":22,"arabic":"كُفْرُهُمْ","translation":"তাদের অবিশ্বাস","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40928,"position":23,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40929,"position":24,"arabic":"خَسَارًۭا","translation":"ক্ষতি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_039_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":40930,"position":25,"arabic":"٣٩","translation":"(৩৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":40,"arabic":"قُلْ أَرَءَيْتُمْ شُرَكَآءَكُمُ ٱلَّذِينَ تَدْعُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ أَرُونِى مَاذَا خَلَقُوا۟ مِنَ ٱلْأَرْضِ أَمْ لَهُمْ شِرْكٌۭ فِى ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ أَمْ ءَاتَيْنَٰهُمْ كِتَٰبًۭا فَهُمْ عَلَىٰ بَيِّنَتٍۢ مِّنْهُ ۚ بَلْ إِن يَعِدُ ٱلظَّٰلِمُونَ بَعْضُهُم بَعْضًا إِلَّا غُرُورًا","translation":"Say: “Have you ever [really] considered those beings and forces to whom you ascribe a share in God’s divinity, [and] whom you invoke beside God? Show me what it is that they have created on earth - or do [you claim that] they have a share in [govern­ing] the heavens?” Have We ever vouchsafed them a divine writ on which they could rely as evidence [in support of their views]? Nay, [the hope which] the evildoers hold out to one another [is] nothing but a delusion.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3700.mp3","surahId":35,"words":[{"id":41806,"position":1,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41807,"position":2,"arabic":"أَرَءَيْتُمْ","translation":"\"তোমরা (ভেবে) দেখেছো কি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41808,"position":3,"arabic":"شُرَكَآءَكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদের শরীকদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41809,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41810,"position":5,"arabic":"تَدْعُونَ","translation":"তোমরা ডেকে থাকো","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41811,"position":6,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41812,"position":7,"arabic":"دُونِ","translation":"ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41813,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহকে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41814,"position":9,"arabic":"أَرُونِى","translation":"আমাকে দেখাও","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41815,"position":10,"arabic":"مَاذَا","translation":"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41816,"position":11,"arabic":"خَلَقُوا۟","translation":"তারা সৃষ্টি করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41817,"position":12,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"কিছু","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41818,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"পৃথিবীতে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41819,"position":14,"arabic":"أَمْ","translation":"বা","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41820,"position":15,"arabic":"لَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের জন্যে (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41821,"position":16,"arabic":"شِرْكٌۭ","translation":"অংশ","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41822,"position":17,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41823,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশের","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41824,"position":19,"arabic":"أَمْ","translation":"অথবা","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41825,"position":20,"arabic":"ءَاتَيْنَـٰهُمْ","translation":"তাদেরকে আমরা দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41826,"position":21,"arabic":"كِتَـٰبًۭا","translation":"কোনো কিতাব","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41827,"position":22,"arabic":"فَهُمْ","translation":"অতঃপর তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41828,"position":23,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"(প্রতিষ্ঠিত) উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41829,"position":24,"arabic":"بَيِّنَتٍۢ","translation":"প্রমাণের","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41830,"position":25,"arabic":"مِّنْهُ ۚ","translation":"তা থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41832,"position":26,"arabic":"بَلْ","translation":"বরং","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41833,"position":27,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41834,"position":28,"arabic":"يَعِدُ","translation":"প্রতিশ্রুতি দেয়","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41835,"position":29,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمُونَ","translation":"সীমালঙ্ঘনকারীরা","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41836,"position":30,"arabic":"بَعْضُهُم","translation":"তাদের একে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41837,"position":31,"arabic":"بَعْضًا","translation":"অপরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41838,"position":32,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41839,"position":33,"arabic":"غُرُورًا","translation":"ধোঁকা","audioUrl":"wbw/035_040_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":41840,"position":34,"arabic":"٤٠","translation":"(৪০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":41,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ يُمْسِكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلْأَرْضَ أَن تَزُولَا ۚ وَلَئِن زَالَتَآ إِنْ أَمْسَكَهُمَا مِنْ أَحَدٍۢ مِّنۢ بَعْدِهِۦٓ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ حَلِيمًا غَفُورًۭا","translation":"Verily, it is God [alone] who upholds the celestial bodies and the earth, lest they deviate [from their orbits] - for if they should ever deviate, there is none that could uphold them after He will have ceased to do so. [But,] verily, He is ever-forbearing, much-for­giving!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3701.mp3","surahId":35,"words":[{"id":42580,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42581,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42582,"position":3,"arabic":"يُمْسِكُ","translation":"স্হিরভাবে ধরে রেখেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42583,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٰتِ","translation":"আকাশকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42584,"position":5,"arabic":"وَٱلْأَرْضَ","translation":"ও পৃথিবীকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42585,"position":6,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যেন (না)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42586,"position":7,"arabic":"تَزُولَا ۚ","translation":"কক্ষচ্যুত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42588,"position":8,"arabic":"وَلَئِن","translation":"আর অবশ্য যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42589,"position":9,"arabic":"زَالَتَآ","translation":"কক্ষচ্যুত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42590,"position":10,"arabic":"إِنْ","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42591,"position":11,"arabic":"أَمْسَكَهُمَا","translation":"উভয়কে স্হিরভাবে ধরে রাখতে পারবে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42592,"position":12,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"মধ্য হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42593,"position":13,"arabic":"أَحَدٍۢ","translation":"কেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42594,"position":14,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42595,"position":15,"arabic":"بَعْدِهِۦٓ ۚ","translation":"তাঁর পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42597,"position":16,"arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই তিনি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42598,"position":17,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"হলেন","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42599,"position":18,"arabic":"حَلِيمًا","translation":"সহনশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42600,"position":19,"arabic":"غَفُورًۭا","translation":"ক্ষমাশীল","audioUrl":"wbw/035_041_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":42601,"position":20,"arabic":"٤١","translation":"(৪১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":42,"arabic":"وَأَقْسَمُوا۟ بِٱللَّهِ جَهْدَ أَيْمَٰنِهِمْ لَئِن جَآءَهُمْ نَذِيرٌۭ لَّيَكُونُنَّ أَهْدَىٰ مِنْ إِحْدَى ٱلْأُمَمِ ۖ فَلَمَّا جَآءَهُمْ نَذِيرٌۭ مَّا زَادَهُمْ إِلَّا نُفُورًا","translation":"As it is, they [who are averse to the truth often] swear by God with their most solemn oaths that if a warner should ever come to them, they would follow his guidance better than any of the communities [of old had followed the warner sent to them]: but now that a warner has come unto them, [his call] but increases their aversion,","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3702.mp3","surahId":35,"words":[{"id":43294,"position":1,"arabic":"وَأَقْسَمُوا۟","translation":"এবং তারা শপথ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43295,"position":2,"arabic":"بِٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহর (নামে)","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43296,"position":3,"arabic":"جَهْدَ","translation":"কড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43297,"position":4,"arabic":"أَيْمَـٰنِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের শপথসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43298,"position":5,"arabic":"لَئِن","translation":"অবশ্যই যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43299,"position":6,"arabic":"جَآءَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের কাছে আসেন","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43300,"position":7,"arabic":"نَذِيرٌۭ","translation":"কোনো সতর্ককারী","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43301,"position":8,"arabic":"لَّيَكُونُنَّ","translation":"তারা হবে অবশ্যই","audioUrl":"wbw/035_042_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":43302,"position":9,"arabic":"أَهْدَىٰ","transl